short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Corrects a mistake where national headlines accidentally write "Donald Trump" instead of "Florida Man".

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: With the advent of fake news, it is vital that the online "lamestream" media portrays information objectively and factually. In turn, this extension corrects a mistake where (inter)national headlines mistakenly write "Donald Trump" instead of "Florida Man". This more accurately conveys such journalism as to better inform the reader.
